These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, dunhill, pall-mall, game
There 4 different types of food: orange, peach, banana, nectarine
There are 4 different nationalities: french, australian, american, polish
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, purple, brown, ebony
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, begonia, bellflower, rose
4 different games are played: domino, snooker, poker, bridge
4 different pets are kept: fish, cat, rabbit, dog
 1. the montecristo-smoker is the person who likes light-blue##1
 2. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 3. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 4. the australian is on the far right##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 6. the owner of the fish is the dunhill-smoker##1
 7. the person playing snooker is on the left of the american##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 9. the owner of the dog is the person who growsbegonia##1
10. the owner of the cat is on the right of the french##1
11. the person playing domino is the dunhill-smoker##1
12. the owner of the cat is the person who growsbellflower##1
13. the person playing bridge is on the right of the game-smoker##1
14. the person playing snooker is the game-smoker##1
15. the person playing bridge is the american##1
16. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the french##1
17. the pall-mall-smoker is the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4      |
| Cigar      | montecristo       | game      | pall-mall       | dunhill    |
| Food         | orange    | nectarine    | peach      | banana    |
| Nationality           | polish | french       | american | australian     |
| Color   | light-blue         | brown  | ebony      | purple     |
| Flower   | begonia          | rose     | bellflower       | balloon-flower |
| Game         | poker       | snooker | bridge       | domino   |
| Pet     | dog     | rabbit  | cat         | fish   |

