The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, june, february, november
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, lemonade, tea
House: victorian, craftsman, futuristic, palace
4 different games are played: domino, billiard, canasta, backgammon
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, azalea, tulip, rose
