 1. the musician is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 2. the person playing billiard is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 3. the coach is on the left of the police-officer##1
 4. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the palace house is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the victorian house is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the police-officer##1
11. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
12. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
13. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
14. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
15. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
16. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
17. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3      |      4      |
