 7. the art-deco house is on the left of the colonial house##1
 8. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
10. the person who growszinnia is the futuristic house##1
11. the person playing billiard is the malaysian##1
12. the turkish is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
13. the colonial house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
14. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
15. the person driving the trike is the person who's birthday is in august##1
16. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
17. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
